{"type":"message","id":"6ccdd81c","parentId":"0c02fd7c","timestamp":"2026-03-05T03:33:37.411Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"从日志里看到了关键信息：`[wecom] webhook registered at /wecom for account default`，说明企业微信channel已经正常注册了。让我再检查一下channels.status来确认。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"企业微信channel设置正常 ✅\n\n从日志可以看到：\n- webhook已注册在 `/wecom` 路径\n- 插件已加载并启用\n\n配置项都齐全：token、encodingAESKey、enabled都已设置。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ark","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-code","usage":{"input":30446,"output":142,"cacheRead":7992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38580,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772681610815}}
{"type":"message","id":"03ec787c","parentId":"6ccdd81c","timestamp":"2026-03-05T04:00:37.429Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"bc004eaf-eaa5-416f-b291-6e640a3543bd\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"sender\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-03-05 12:00 GMT+8] 这个API该从哪里获取"},{"type":"image","data":"","mimeType":"image/png"}],"timestamp":1772683237426}}
{"type":"message","id":"1532da83","parentId":"03ec787c","timestamp":"2026-03-05T04:00:49.745Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问这个API该从哪里获取，截图显示的是Brave Search API key。我需要告诉用户如何获取Brave Search API key。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Brave Search API key 可以从这里获取：\n\n1. 访问 Brave Search API 官网：https://brave.com/search/api/\n2. 点击 \"Get API Key\" 或类似按钮\n3. 按照提示注册/登录 Brave 账户\n4. 创建一个新的 API key\n5. 复制生成的 key 粘贴到配置中\n\n另外，也可以直接设置环境变量 `BRAVE_API_KEY` 来使用，不需要在配置文件里保存。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ark","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-code","usage":{"input":32845,"output":168,"cacheRead":6200,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39213,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772683237428}}
{"type":"message","id":"4619b2dd","parentId":"1532da83","timestamp":"2026-03-05T04:00:49.785Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Brave Search API key 可以从这里获取：\n\n1. 访问 Brave Search API 官网：https://brave.com/search/api/\n2. 点击 \"Get API Key\" 或类似按钮\n3. 按照提示注册/登录 Brave 账户\n4. 创建一个新的 API key\n5. 复制生成的 key 粘贴到配置中\n\n另外，也可以直接设置环境变量 `BRAVE_API_KEY` 来使用，不需要在配置文件里保存。"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772683249785}}
