{"type":"message","id":"5ff10877","parentId":"b68326f3","timestamp":"2026-03-05T04:04:20.266Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了！有个 `openclaw-web-search` 插件，描述是\"OpenClaw web search plugin via Zhipu AI API, accessible from within China\"，正好符合用户需求。让我给用户推荐这个。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了！有个专门为国内用户准备的搜索插件：\n\n**openclaw-web-search** - 通过智谱AI API实现的网页搜索，国内可直接访问\n\n你可以安装它：\n```bash\nopenclaw plugin install openclaw-web-search\n```\n\n然后配置智谱AI的API key就可以用了。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ark","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-code","usage":{"input":6642,"output":170,"cacheRead":39224,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46036,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772683446756}}
{"type":"message","id":"192fb94c","parentId":"5ff10877","timestamp":"2026-03-05T05:19:24.527Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-03-05 13:19 GMT+8] 我在查看这些你的技能，这里的blocked是什么意思"},{"type":"image","data":"","mimeType":"image/png"}],"timestamp":1772687964519}}
{"type":"message","id":"c4946934","parentId":"192fb94c","timestamp":"2026-03-05T05:19:35.020Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问\"blocked\"是什么意思。从截图看，这些技能显示\"blocked\"，下面还有\"Missing: bin:op\"、\"Missing: bin:memo, os:darwin\"这样的提示。\n\n意思很清楚：这些技能被阻止使用了，因为缺少必要的依赖（比如特定的命令行工具或操作系统）。\n\n比如：\n- 1password 技能需要 `op` 命令行工具\n- apple-notes 需要 macOS 系统和 `memo` 工具\n- apple-reminders 需要 macOS 系统和 `remindctl` 工具\n- bear-notes 需要 macOS 系统和 `grizzly` 工具\n\n这些都是系统级依赖，缺失的话技能就无法正常工作，所以显示为 blocked。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\"blocked\" 表示这些技能被阻止使用了，原因是缺少必要的依赖：\n\n从截图可以看到：\n- **1password** - 缺少 `op` 命令行工具\n- **apple-notes** - 需要 macOS 系统 + `memo` 工具\n- **apple-reminders** - 需要 macOS 系统 + `remindctl` 工具\n- **bear-notes** - 需要 macOS 系统 + `grizzly` 工具\n\n这些都是系统级依赖，缺失的话技能无法正常工作，所以显示为 blocked。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ark","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-code","usage":{"input":42936,"output":456,"cacheRead":3384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46776,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772687964524}}
